* metadata.dts
* Canonical DotTalk++ metadata lane bootstrap.
* Metadata DBFs live under DATA\METADATA and use the shared CDX/LMDB roots
* under DATA\INDEXES\METADATA and DATA\LMDB\METADATA.
* This script assumes paths are resolved relative to the runtime DATA root.
SETPATH DBF metadata
SETPATH INDEXES indexes\metadata
SETPATH LMDB lmdb\metadata
